# ==============================================================================
# .dockerignore — SpectraMind V50 (NeurIPS 2025 Ariel Data Challenge)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Purpose:
#   • Prevent unnecessary files from bloating Docker images
#   • Mirror .gitignore + .dvcignore for consistency
#   • Keep Docker context lean, CI-safe, and reproducible
#   • Ensure only source + configs + required assets make it into the image
# ==============================================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python build & cache
